headline: Should You Buy CrowdStrike Before Nov. 26? Here's What History Says.
summary: CrowdStrike (NASDAQ: CRWD) experienced the worst of times this year.  CrowdStrike immediately took action, issuing a fix to the problem in about an hour, and in the weeks that followed put into place measures to prevent a similar event from happening again.  As a result, customers and investors seem to have maintained their faith in the company.
